{"id":3760,"date":"2019-09-06T10:42:57","date_gmt":"2019-09-06T03:42:57","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/tintuc8.muathemewordpress.net\/?p=3760"},"modified":"2021-05-25T20:31:55","modified_gmt":"2021-05-25T13:31:55","slug":"7-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-de-tiet-kiem-khong-gian-trong-can-ho-nho","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/7-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-de-tiet-kiem-khong-gian-trong-can-ho-nho\/","title":{"rendered":"7 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng gian trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 nh\u1ecf"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1i n\u1edbi ra g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 1 trong nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1ed1ng trong m\u1ed9t c\u0103n h\u1ed9 nh\u1ecf, ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p, h\u1eb3n vi\u1ec7c b\u00e0i tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng sinh ho\u1ea1t s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng lo l\u1eafng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 b\u00e9 nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<p><strong>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc t\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u0103n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc t\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u0103n \u0111\u1ef1ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng gian khi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea5y. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, b\u00ecnh hoa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 trang tr\u00ed cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng th\u00eam sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414510-84748610-097d4a3fca8ad3cab72b0f0d8d2914b6d6887606-1500-1-1551072631-728-38b8beff96-1551253031-1-145429165.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-43169\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414510-84748610-097d4a3fca8ad3cab72b0f0d8d2914b6d6887606-1500-1-1551072631-728-38b8beff96-1551253031-1-145429165-691x1024.jpg\" alt=\"10414510-84748610-097d4a3fca8ad3cab72b0f0d8d2914b6d6887606-1500-1-1551072631-728-38b8beff96-1551253031-1-145429165\" width=\"567\" height=\"840\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 treo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec chi\u1ebfm qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u1ecf n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee9 g\u00ec c\u0169ng b\u00e0y ra s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn n\u01a1i \u1edf c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u00eam ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p. \u0110\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, t\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc m\u00f3c treo sau c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda, t\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng sinh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1ec9. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2u.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414260-depositphotos43365321xl-2015-1549655448-728-b4a22ad3d4-1551253031-150819976.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-43170\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414260-depositphotos43365321xl-2015-154