 m\u1eaft.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414210-screenshot2019-02-05at53641pm-1549406219-728-b7e492f5e1-1551253031-151701157.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-43173\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414210-screenshot2019-02-05at53641pm-1549406219-728-b7e492f5e1-1551253031-151701157.jpg\" alt=\"10414210-screenshot2019-02-05at53641pm-1549406219-728-b7e492f5e1-1551253031-151701157\" width=\"567\" height=\"545\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian d\u01b0\u1edbi gi\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u01b0u tr\u1eef \u0111\u1ed3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng gian l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c trong ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414110-cg18bed10073745-bed-risersv2rgb-1549470722-728-872203261e-1551253031-151925551.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-43174\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10414110-cg18bed10073745-bed-risersv2rgb-1549470722-728-872203261e-1551253031-151925551.jpg\" alt=\"10414110-cg18bed10073745-bed-risersv2rgb-1549470722-728-872203261e-1551253031-151925551\" width=\"567\" height=\"567\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>D\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh nh\u1ecf c\u1ee1 v\u1eeba thay v\u00ec 2 c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m di\u1ec7n t\u00edch<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/10413960-71b8zbajeglsl1200-1549468547-728-1039d05e3c-1551253031-15203767.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-43175\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/0